### 3. Modification de `App.tsx` — handleAnalyze

Apres la ligne `const updatedHistory = db.add(result);` (ligne 383), ajouter un fire-and-forget :

```typescript
// Pre-generation en arriere-plan
setMegaStatus('generating');
megaGenerate(url).then(cache => {
  if (cache) {
    const preGenerated = { status: 'completed', generatedAt: new Date().toISOString(), ...cache };
    // Mettre a jour history[0] (dernier audit ajoute)
    setHistory(prev => {
      const updated = { ...prev[0], preGenerated };
      db.update(0, updated);
      return [updated, ...prev.slice(1)];
    });
    setAnalysisData(prev => prev ? { ...prev, preGenerated } : prev);
    setMegaStatus('completed');
  } else {
    setMegaStatus('failed');
  }
}).catch(() => setMegaStatus('failed'));
```

Nouveau state : `const [megaStatus, setMegaStatus] = useState<MegaGenerationStatus>('idle');`

